name: Sick Minded
description:
It is the story of suppressing human natural instincts. It will specifically end up in compulsive sexual behavior, mainly caused by cultures tainted with religion, unfounded epidemic beliefs, pornography addiction, etc. It leads to sick and uncontrollable desires in individuals, and the victims will end up hurting themselves and others - mentally and physically. 
Ignorance and suppression of whatever that is NATURAL is always a bad idea.
